        <h1>4. Ingress Controller</h1>
      </div>

      <p>
        The ALB forwards traffic to the <b>EKS worker nodes</b> in the private subnet.
        The <b>Ingress Controller</b> (for example, Nginx) running as a pod receives
        the request and performs <b>Layer 7 routing</b> based on the URL path
        (such as <code>/api</code> vs <code>/auth</code>).
      </p>

